channel.title: Owners these days sicken me
channel.description:
I went onto a server I've been playing for a while to find out my password has been changed. I log in with a new account and ask why, and the owner comes up to me and says "lol source changed". I said "no, source change != password change" and he goes "i kno more than u, i can code" so I say "Okay, in programming terms, what is an object?"
The reply: "like a bank n shit"
